JErgometer
""""""""""

1. Dependencies

JErgometer depends on the RXTX library used to communicate over a serial connection.
Install the corresponding package of your distribution (Ubuntu/Debian: librxtx-java)
or download the library from
	http://rxtx.qbang.org/
and "install" it manually.

Afterwards configure the path to the RXTXcomm.jar in build.properties.
Alternatively, you can run
	./configure
which tries to automatically detect the path.


2. Compilation

To compile JErgometer run
	ant create_linux_package
A jar file is generated and


